{"tid":17323,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"會員 濛濛 入黎","createTime":"2016-12-01T19:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T05:59:05.000Z","uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"76f910274e69fa6713a5e119c0b8cd8fb6b04a59","tid":17323,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:13:55.000Z","msg":"我愛你"},{"pid":"7e692a6aa15429a8373b47298b380cf0c816a201","tid":17323,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:14:19.000Z","msg":"我想做你筆友"},{"pid":"fe52dc2d28bcbdb457ed921a0299e92ea836afe8","tid":17323,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:21:16.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"0df3962ff9f0ec581fb53378260b3e336e22b8cc","tid":17323,"uid":17282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:55:24.000Z","msg":"不好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">留地址比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"c614861f846228d50304f8fd3d9f7ef68d2c7d6a","tid":17323,"uid":17282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">留地址比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了"},{"pid":"9377b789a2b101a7baaca9834755ba3ab88a3ba9","tid":17323,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:52:15.000Z","msg":"由細到大，我都唔鐘意講野，特別對住D岩岩識既人。但熟左可以講好多野。好多人覺得我好難接近，但其實我唔係。只係我一緊張個時就會扮COOL，掩飾自己緊張。<br />\n<br />\n其實對屋企人都係，明明好惜佢地，但唔知點解表現出黎就係衰仔，無禮貌。<br />\n<br />\n由初中到U GRAD出黎做左幾年野，一直都想識女仔，前前後後認真嘗試中學APPROACH過兩個，大學兩至三個，個個都係，一開始好好傾-＞自己FF人地對自己都有意思-＞忍唔住WHATSAPP（親口問都唔敢）約佢-＞永遠唔得閒-＞人地驚左你避你。仲有我係個D第一眼見佢就鐘意左佢個D人黎。我大學個時好摺，個D女仔全部都係上堂識。<br />\n<br />\n又唔係話無女仔鐘意我，但次次都係我有TARGET時出現，中學有1-2個，大學都有1-2個，旅行有1個。<br />\n<br />\n出左黎做野唔駛講，男人工平時返工無女仔，OT到8,9點就返屋企食飯，禮拜六日難得放假但係都要讀書進修，有時間打下機踢波都係唔會見到女仔。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，咁我唯有試下DOWNLOAD D APP黎睇下上網識唔識到，真係想認真識，一係我驚個女仔係雞，一係個女仔驚我係PLAYBOY，好唔容易搵到兩三個拎到電話，有一個係大學生，出黎見過幾次，但係因為我識佢個時佢同BF岩岩分手，搵我黎解佢寂莫，好失望，雖然無講到出黎，但男仔想得呢D APP一係想玩 一係想搵個GF陪。但係佢就要扮到搵朋友甘搵我解悶。。第二同三個就係APP到傾左幾日，我覺得幾好傾，但一拎到WHATSAPP之後唔知忙定咩，覆得好慢。。。"},{"pid":"7a7cc4b3a538ba0b5396e721246eead89994e966","tid":17323,"uid":43884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:01:00.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"009f9e190bc155a7491b81fb8e3b2debe715c00c","tid":17323,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:11:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cec70c5a1440779cf72f545311eef237b2cf3cf5","tid":17323,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"???<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59391d5a8b6748492b20dad7afc08d89cdd59bea","tid":17323,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253bbdcc1099079d07c3a23b088fa830c0d0d770","tid":17323,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bfee791a057a88b9d6e244e241b3d88e8dcc55","tid":17323,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"253bbdcc1099079d07c3a23b088fa830c0d0d770","tid":17323,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屎忽痕？"},{"pid":"e8a2cb230303176967a9d652971ce9487c47b5e3","tid":17323,"uid"